<H3>
<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-21021" num="9"> DARA's New Director Mennicken on Goals, Research, Budget</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-21021" num="10"> 94WS0096A Duesseldorf HANDELSBLATT in German 12-13 Nov 93 p 23</s>
</F>
