<s docid="FBIS4-44690" num="11"> Decline of Columbus Program</s>
</H4>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS4-44690" num="12"> 94WS0342A Berlin INGENIEUR DIGEST in German May 94 pp 18-19</s>
</F>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS4-44690" num="13"> 94WS0342A</s>
