<H3>
<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-59901" num="8"> NASA Chief Gives News Conference on Joint Space Project</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-59901" num="9"> LD1612184293 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1815 GMT 16 Dec 93</s>
</F>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-59901" num="10"> LD1612184293</s>
