<s docid="FBIS3-59774" num="20"> K. Fusegi, senior specialist, Aerospace Division, Space Station Dept.</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-59774" num="21"> K. Nakao, Aerospace Division, Space Station Dept.</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-59774" num="22"> H. Ban, Aerospace Division, Space Station Dept.</s>

<s docid="FBIS3-59774" num="23"> T. Ohashi, Aerospace Division, Space Station Dept.</s>

